Package com.safenetinc.luna.provider.keygen Description

JCA-compliant implementation of key generator classes to create new Luna secret keys and public/private key pairs for LunaProvider. Only accessed from Luna provider framework. You should just refer to these classes for an idea of the provided mechanisms.
